## Decisions Made
- watchdog auto-promotes the next queued candidate set on stale demotion (FIFO is mechanical, not judgment) — matches reference/execution-details.md.
- Budget alerts are deduplicated against existing open_alerts by (type, work_item_id, budget) tuple to keep tick idempotent across runs.
- Always bumps watchdog-jobs.json revision (last_tick_at update) even when nothing else changed, so callers can verify the tick ran.

